======
README
WD-API docs
======

This is a short readme on how to use the internal docs of the wd-api. These are
not consumer docs. These are dev docs so that ideas and methodologies can be
shared with others.

All changes are to be made in the 'source' directory.

To learn how to use sphinx, start here:
http://sphinx-doc.org/tutorial.html

Sphinx is installed through pip so you should not have to manually install it
into your virtualenv.

Building the docs:
------------------
To build the docs, run this command from this directory:
gmake html

Using Autodoc:
--------------
For a detailed explanation of Autodoc, check here:
http://sphinx-doc.org/ext/autodoc.html#module-sphinx.ext.autodoc
